QuestData.Title: Quack for Your Life
QuestData.Description:
<This duckling is quacking frantically. If someone doesn't help it, the gorlocs will surely get annoyed!>
<Maybe the ecologists would know how to help it?>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Bubbled Duckling back to the Ecologists' Camp.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Bubbled Duckling back to the Ecologists' Camp.

Objectives.Objective: Bubbled Duckling brought to the Ecologist's Camp
